OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A hosepipe ban is to come into force in
OL,6, parts of southern England after a lack 
OL,7, of rainfall and extreme temperatures.  
OL,9,FThe restrictions for Southern Water    
OL,10,Fcustomers in Hampshire and the Isle of 
OL,11,FWight will start from 5 August.        
OL,13,FUsing hosepipes to water gardens, clean
OL,14,Fcars, fill ornamental ponds and        
OL,15,Fswimming pools will not be allowed.    
OL,17,FThe firm said the ban was a "vital     
OL,18,Fstep" to protect the habitats of the   
OL,19,FRiver Test and the River Itchen where  
OL,20,Fit extracts water.                     
